In the Kostroma and Magadan regions, the concept of "social entrepreneurship" and the areas of support for social entrepreneurship are recommended for consolidation in the regulatory and legal field.
All proposals from the regions will be taken into account in the preparation of state support programs for small and medium-sized enterprises, and the most important will receive development in the form of specific bills.
